\f1\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf2 \expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
A simple basil-infused pasta sauce is one of our favorite ways to showcase sweet summer tomatoes. Here, we're adding white wine to the sauce for depth, then tossing in al dente spaghetti and pecorino cheese. Pieces of ethereally creamy burrata take this glorious pasta to the next level. 
