\cf3 Tips:\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl280\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec4 - Be sure to read through the entire recipe before you begin cooking. Trust us\'97you'll be glad you did! \
- Starchy pasta cooking water will give your sauce a perfect consistency and help it to cling to the noodles. Keep adding it until the sauce is silky\'97you may need more than you think. \
- Burrata is delicate, so be sure to handle it gently. Discard only the watery liquid from the container, not cheese solids.\cf3 \outl0\strokewidth0 \
